    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Column {width=\"30%\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "### Observations\n",
        "\n",
        "- Weekend days show higher bill variability.\n",
        "- Dinner generates larger bills than lunch.\n",
        "- Tip percentage distribution is relatively stable with some high outliers.\n",
        "- Larger party sizes produce larger total tips but similar percentages.\n",
        "\n",
        "## Row {height=40%}\n",
        "\n",
        "### Column {width=\"50%\"}"
      ],
      "id": "b3ce2c2d"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "px.histogram(\n",
        "    tips,\n",
        "    x=\"tip_pct\",\n",
        "    nbins=20,\n",
        "    color_discrete_sequence=[\"#0F766E\"],\n",
        "    title=\"Distribution of Tip Percentages\"\n",
        ")"
      ],
      "id": "e9e1570f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
